## Ingredients

- [ ] 1/2 - 1 lb. Asparagus
- [ ] 1/4 tsp salt
- [ ] (Optional) garlic clove, lemon peel, etc.

## Recipe

1. Boil 3/4-1" water in a large, covered skillet. Add salt and optional clove, lemon peel, etc.
1. Chop the inedible bottom of the Asparagus off
1. Cover and cook the asparagus for 5-7 minutes
1. Add additional salt, pepper, lemon juice, oil, butter, etc. before serving
